    <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 text-base md:text-lg max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mb-16" data-i18n="journey.subtitle">
      In drei einfachen Schritten: vom Problem zu mehr Anfragen.
    </p>

    <div class="relative space-y-16 md:space-y-24 pl-12 md:pl-0">
      <!-- Progress line -->
      <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-700" aria-hidden="true">
        <div id="timeline-progress" class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 w-full bg-gradient-to-b from-yellow-500 to-orange-500 rounded-full" style="height: 0%"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 1: Problem -->
      <article class="relative md:grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] md:gap-10">
        <div class="absolute left-0 md:relative flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-black border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-orange-500"></span>
          </span>
          <h3 class="md:hidden text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400" data-i18n="pas.problem.title">Problem</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="hidden md:block text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400 mb-6" data-i18n="pas.problem.title">Problem</h3>
          <div class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed" data-i18n="pas.problem.text">
              Kunden suchen bei Google nach dem, was Sie anbieten – und finden Sie nicht. Stattdessen rufen sie die Konkurrenz an.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Step 2: Herausforderung -->
      <article class="relative md:grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] md:gap-10">
        <div class="absolute left-0 md:relative flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-black border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-orange-500"></span>
          </span>
          <h3 class="md:hidden text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400" data-i18n="pas.agitate.title">Herausforderung</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="hidden md:block text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400 mb-6" data-i18n="pas.agitate.title">Herausforderung</h3>
          <div class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed" data-i18n="pas.agitate.text">
              Jeden Tag gehen Anfragen an andere Firmen. Sie merken es oft gar nicht – bis der Kalender leer bleibt und das Telefon still ist.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Step 3: Lösung -->
      <article class="relative md:grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] md:gap-10">
        <div class="absolute left-0 md:relative flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <span class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-black border border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-orange-500"></span>
          </span>
          <h3 class="md:hidden text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400" data-i18n="pas.solution.title">Unsere Lösung</h3>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="hidden md:block text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-yellow-500 dark:text-yellow-400 mb-6" data-i18n="pas.solution.title">Unsere Lösung</h3>
          <div class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
